## tool-tmux: shell tool

tmux_new <name>: creates a new session with name <name>, current session is the new session
tmux_exec <name> <command>: runs shell command
tmux_ls: list sessions
tmux_kill_session(<session_id>): kills session <session_id>
tmux_kill_server: kill all tmux sessions
tmux_history: list of commands you have run
tmux_history_limit: set maximum commands
tmux_call_limit: view or set session limit